OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FFree impartial news should be
OL,8,Fprioritised by governments as a part
OL,9,Fof "an essential cornerstone of a
OL,10,Fhealthy, informed democracy," the
OL,11,Fformer Director of News and Current
OL,12,FAffairs at ITV said during a speech at
OL,13,Fthe Royal Television Society's 2025
OL,14,FJournalism Awards.
OL,16,FMichael Jermey called for the
OL,17,Fgovernment and Ofcom to ensure viewers
OL,18,Fwill continue to have access to free-
OL,19,Fto-view impartial news over the next
OL,20,Fdecade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
