OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FHe said they needed to
OL,8,F"unapologetically in favour of
OL,9,Fsustaining homegrown British Public
OL,10,FService Broadcasting, even in the face
OL,11,Fof potential opposition from powerful
OL,12,Finternational players ` most of them
OL,13,Fbased in the United States."
OL,15,FSpecifically, Mr Jeremy called for a
OL,16,Fnew permanent Royal Charter and better
OL,17,Ffunding for the BBC to insulate the
OL,18,Fcorporation from politics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
