OL,7,FMr Jeremy was the Director of News and
OL,8,FCurrent Affairs at ITV for 16 years
OL,9,Fbefore standing down at the end of
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FMr Jeremy's full speech can be seen
OL,13,Fbelow.
OL,15,F"The 70-year success of television
OL,16,Fjournalism in the UK has been
OL,17,Funderpinned by an environment which
OL,18,Fwas deliberately created to ensure
OL,19,Fthat British viewers would have free
OL,20,Faccess to excellent, impartial
OL,21,Fbroadcast journalism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
