OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FAnd it's the vital importance of
OL,8,Fsustaining that environment, in the
OL,9,Finterests of democracy, that I want to
OL,10,Faddress tonight.
OL,12,FThe measures that created our
OL,13,Fbroadcast ecology were introduced
OL,14,Fincrementally over years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
