OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FThe television licence fee funding the
OL,8,FBBC, the ITV Public Service
OL,9,FBroadcasting licences, the creation of
OL,10,FChannel 4 and then Five and the
OL,11,Fnurturing of the independent
OL,12,Fproduction sector alongside them, the
OL,13,Fcommercial climate that assisted the
OL,14,Flaunch of Sky News.
OL,16,FThe environment created helped make
OL,17,Fthis country an international centre
OL,18,Fof excellence for news and current
OL,19,Faffairs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
