OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FOur part of the industry ` with its
OL,8,Femphasis on impartiality, solid facts
OL,9,Fand eye-witness reporting -- has
OL,10,Fhelped underpin our democracy.
OL,12,FThat's not something that has happened
OL,13,Fin every country ` not even in every
OL,14,Fwestern democracy.
OL,16,FWe've seen this evening that the
OL,17,Fjournalism is as good as ever ` both
OL,18,Fnationally and in our vitally
OL,19,Fimportant regional programmes too.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
