OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FBut the environment, created and
OL,8,Fnurtured over decades should not be
OL,9,Ftaken for granted.
OL,11,FIn some ways we're living in a golden
OL,12,Fage of television. It's possible to
OL,13,Fpay to watch more entertainment, sport
OL,14,Fand drama than ever before.
OL,16,FBut this positive, commercially driven
OL,17,Fexplosion in choice doesn't do
OL,18,Fanything to guarantee that high
OL,19,Fquality, impartial broadcast news and
OL,20,Fcurrent affairs will remain available
OL,21,Ffree to every citizen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
