OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FAs the economics of television change
OL,8,Fand some of the traditional sources of
OL,9,Frevenue become much more uncertain, we
OL,10,Fneed to find new ways to support the
OL,11,Fthings we have always valued.
OL,13,FThere is a need for policy makers to
OL,14,Ftake a strategic view of the sector as
OL,15,Fa whole and then take action to
OL,16,Fguarantee its future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
