OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FFirst, there needs to be a stable and
OL,8,Frobust funding mechanism for the BBC,
OL,9,Fensuring its journalism is properly
OL,10,Fsupported. In my view it's time, too,
OL,11,Ffor the BBC to have a permanent Royal
OL,12,FCharter as a first step to further
OL,13,Finsulate it from the vagaries of
OL,14,Fpolitics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
