OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FBut, it's equally important that the
OL,8,Fcommercial Public Service
OL,9,FBroadcasters` ITV, Channel 4 and Five
OL,10,F-- are nurtured and assisted in
OL,11,Fcontinuing to provide engaging,
OL,12,Fimpartial news and current affairs.
OL,13,FNot just at the national level but in
OL,14,Fthe regions and nations too.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
