OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FThe regulator needs to make robust use
OL,8,Fof all the powers granted in the Media
OL,9,FAct to ensure that PSB content is
OL,10,Fprominently available to audiences of
OL,11,Fall ages, whatever platform they
OL,12,Fchoose to use. And it's equally
OL,13,Fimportant that those platforms treat
OL,14,FPSBs fairly and don't try to seek
OL,15,Fshares of their commercial revenues.
OL,16,FThe regulator needs to be robust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
