OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FBut policy makers should go further
OL,8,Fstill and ask what more can they do to
OL,9,Fensure free-to-watch impartial news
OL,10,Fand other PSB content continues to
OL,11,Fthrive in our rapidly changing world.
OL,13,FFor example, should tax credits,
OL,14,Fcurrently offered for 'high-end'
OL,15,Fproduction, be extended to help with
OL,16,Fimpartial, commercial news?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
