OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FAnd -- although I'm quite sure it
OL,8,Fwould be unpopular in some quarters --
OL,9,F should the big digital platforms,
OL,10,Fthat benefit economically from news
OL,11,Fand other commercial public service
OL,12,Fcontent, help to pay for it?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
