OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FStrong independent, impartial news and
OL,8,Fcurrent affairs -- of the sort we've
OL,9,Fseen tonight ` should not be seen as
OL,10,Fan optional 'nice to have' but rather
OL,11,Fas one of the essential cornerstones
OL,12,Fof a healthy, informed democracy.
OL,13,FSustaining it and enhancing it over
OL,14,Fthe decade ahead should be a national
OL,15,Fpriority embraced by our industry, by
OL,16,Fan energetic and active regulator and
OL,17,Fby Government and Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
