OL,7,FI think that the work so many people
OL,8,Fin this room do serves a vital public
OL,9,Fpurpose. I'm full of admiration for
OL,10,Fall you do. We've seen so much good,
OL,11,Fenterprising journalism tonight.
OL,12,FThere's lots to be positive about.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
