OL,3,CFormer ITV News chief calls for new
OL,4,CBBC Royal Charter to enhance UK
OL,5,Cjournalism
OL,7,FBut, we need to ensure, that more than
OL,8,F70 years after the first TV news
OL,9,Fbroadcasts, we remain a country that
OL,10,Fcan confidently guarantee that every
OL,11,Fviewer and citizen ` whether they're
OL,12,Fwatching television or living in an
OL,13,Fentirely digital world -- will
OL,14,Fcontinue to have free access to a
OL,15,Frange of high quality, independent and
OL,16,Fimpartial broadcast journalism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
