OL,7,FIt's a challenge that must be met.
OL,8,FIt's important for viewers, for our
OL,9,Fsociety and for the future of our
OL,10,Fdemocracy. And democracy only thrives,
OL,11,Fwhen people who care about it, act to
OL,12,Fprotect it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/19
